 When you talk about computation, how do you think about it?

38:24.080 --> 38:28.960
 Do you think purely on just the switching

38:28.960 --> 38:31.360
 or do you think something a little bit larger scale

38:31.360 --> 38:33.560
 a circuit taken together performing

38:33.560 --> 38:38.280
 the basic arithmetic operations that are then required

38:38.280 --> 38:42.200
 to do the kind of computation that makes up a computer?

