 It has synapses, even synapses are not transistors

42:00.160 --> 42:03.040
 but they are more, they're lower

42:03.040 --> 42:05.360
 on the information processing hierarchy in a sense.

42:05.360 --> 42:08.160
 They do a bulk of the computation

