 So this thalamus is coordinating the activity

1:11:19.120 --> 1:11:21.200
 between the neocortex and the hippocampus

1:11:21.200 --> 1:11:24.040
 and making sure that they talk to each other

1:11:24.040 --> 1:11:25.760
 at the right time and send messages

1:11:25.760 --> 1:11:27.320
 that will be useful to one another.

1:11:27.320 --> 1:11:29.120
 So this all taken together

1:11:29.120 --> 1:11:32.080
 is called the thalamocortical complex.

