1:14:02.440 --> 1:14:05.840
 but the basic idea there is working memory

1:14:05.840 --> 1:14:09.120
 is stored in the dynamical patterns of activity

1:14:09.120 --> 1:14:12.200
 between neurons and you can think

1:14:12.200 --> 1:14:16.040
 of a certain pattern of activity as an attractor,

1:14:16.040 --> 1:14:21.040
 meaning if you put in some signal that's similar enough

1:14:21.040 --> 1:14:26.040
 to other previously experienced signals like that,

1:14:26.440 --> 1:14:29.560
 then you're going to converge to the same network dynamics

1:14:29.560 --> 1:14:34.560
 and you will see these neurons participate

1:14:34.560 --> 1:14:36.200
 in the same network patterns of activity

1:14:36.200 --> 1:14:37.600
 that they have in the past.

1:14:37.600 --> 1:14:39.720
 So you can talk about the probability

1:14:39.720 --> 1:14:42.480
 that different inputs will allow you to converge

1:14:42.480 --> 1:14:44.200
 to different basins of attraction

1:14:44.200 --> 1:14:46.560
 and you might think of that as,

1:14:46.560 --> 1:14:49.880
