1:14:49.880 --> 1:14:53.040
 of activity because last time I saw that face,

1:14:53.040 --> 1:14:55.520
 I was at, you know, some movie

1:14:55.520 --> 1:14:57.480
 and that's a famous person is on the screen

1:14:57.480 --> 1:14:58.320
 or something like that.

1:14:58.320 --> 1:15:00.520
