1:18:41.960 --> 1:18:44.120
 not just in memory formation,

1:18:44.120 --> 1:18:45.360
 although it plays a key role there,

1:18:45.360 --> 1:18:48.240
 but also in just keeping the activity

1:18:48.240 --> 1:18:50.320
 in a useful dynamic range.

1:18:50.320 --> 1:18:52.520
 So you have other plasticity mechanisms,

1:18:52.520 --> 1:18:54.240
 not just weight update,

1:18:54.240 --> 1:18:56.800
 or at least not on the time scale

1:18:56.800 --> 1:18:58.760
 of many action potentials,

1:18:58.760 --> 1:19:00.200
