1:19:19.640 --> 1:19:21.680
 from looking at something bright right now.

1:19:21.680 --> 1:19:23.840
 So I need to tone that down, you know?

1:19:24.960 --> 1:19:28.080
 There's also another really important mechanism

1:19:28.080 --> 1:19:30.520
 in learning, it's called meta plasticity.

1:19:30.520 --> 1:19:35.360
