 So nowhere am I arguing that in all of the vast parameter

2:19:15.600 --> 2:19:18.080
 space of everything that could conceivably exist

2:19:18.080 --> 2:19:20.680
 in the multiverse of nature,

2:19:20.680 --> 2:19:23.320
 there is this one point in parameter space

2:19:23.320 --> 2:19:25.160
 where complexity arises.

2:19:25.160 --> 2:19:26.680
 I doubt it.

