 That would be a shameful waste of resources, it seems.

2:19:31.160 --> 2:19:34.720
 But it might be that we reside at one place

2:19:34.720 --> 2:19:38.480
 in parameter space that has been adapted

2:19:38.480 --> 2:19:40.080
 through an evolutionary process

2:19:40.080 --> 2:19:43.200
 to allow us to make certain technologies

2:19:43.200 --> 2:19:47.120
 that allow our particular kind of universe to arise

2:19:47.120 --> 2:19:49.800
 and sort of achieve the things it does.

2:19:49.800 --> 2:19:52.720
 See, I wonder if nature in this kind of discussion,

2:19:52.720 --> 2:19:55.720
 if nature is a catalyst for innovation

2:19:55.720 --> 2:19:57.680
 or if it's a ceiling for innovation.

